5.plot: In 'Ergens Onderweg' Sam Gooris takes his son Kenji to the beer festival in Munich for some quality time. Now that he is still Minister of Defence, Pieter De Crem finds it high time that all able-bodied men in Belgium join the army. Gunter Lamoot has a 'Vraag van vandaag' for Mega Mindy. Top chef Peter Goossens can do something special and would like to show it to the viewers.
